_sText:
This is a surf skill map.
There are 3 levels. The first level is medium, 2nd is hard and 3 is really hard.
There is a time limit of 3 - 4 minutes (can't remeber), then everyone gets tele to jail. If you make it to the end, you get teleported to another room with a awp, you must awp your enemies before they can get to the button which kills you.

Best results for:
sv_airaccelerate 100 - 200
